caption:
Boundaries aren’t just about keeping others out—they’re about keeping yourself intact. 🌻

✔️ Some people will expect you to hold space for them in ways they never would for you.
✔️ Setting boundaries isn’t selfish; it’s self-respect.
✔️ You don’t need to explain your limits to people who only benefit from you not having them.
